Director: Kurt Wimmer
Studio: Dimension
Synopsis:
Equilibrium is set in the futuristic, and dystopian city-state of Libria.
The film explains how, in the early years of the 21st century, a 
devastating Third World War breaks out, the impact of which brings 
civilizations across the planet to their knees. After the war ends, world
leaders fear that the human race cannot possibly survive 
a Fourth World War, and so set about building a new society 
which is free of conflict.
Run Time: 107 minutes
